index.html:602:                            <span class="lang-text en">More than a store. An urban freshness anchor.</span>
index.html:612:                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-tomato"><span class="lang-text cn">店仓一体化</span><span class="lang-text en">Store-Warehouse Operations</span><span class="lang-text tw">店倉一體化</span><span class="lang-text jp">店舗・倉庫機能</span></h3>
index.html:613:                                <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed text-sm"><span class="lang-text cn">前场负责品牌体验与连带购买，后场作为隐形前置仓，3-5分钟内完成线上合单出货，实现最高坪效。</span><span class="lang-text en">Front builds trust and basket size; back acts as a micro-warehouse completing digital orders in 3-5 mins.</span></p>
index.html:616:                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-leaf"><span class="lang-text cn">品类极致丰富</span><span class="lang-text en">Deep Assortment</span><span class="lang-text tw">品類極致豐富</span><span class="lang-text jp">究極の品揃え</span></h3>
index.html:617:                                <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed text-sm"><span class="lang-text cn">从鲜活水产、有机蔬果到全球进口零食，全场景满足高端社区家庭的日常采买需求。</span><span class="lang-text en">From live seafood to imported snacks, fulfilling every daily need for premium communities.</span></p>
index.html:620:                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white"><span class="lang-text cn">精准选址</span><span class="lang-text en">Strategic Location</span><span class="lang-text tw">精準選址</span><span class="lang-text jp">戦略的な立地</span></h3>
index.html:621:                                <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed text-sm"><span class="lang-text cn">优先布局高密度中高收入住区腹地或核心商圈边缘，确保到店体验与极速配送双重引流。</span><span class="lang-text en">Placed near dense premium neighborhoods to ensure both foot traffic and rapid delivery appeal.</span></p>
