index.html:644:                            <span class="lang-text en">Micro-fulfillment hubs embedded in local blocks — fastest last 100 meters.</span>
index.html:655:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4"><span class="lang-text cn">高密度覆盖</span><span class="lang-text en">Hyper-Local</span><span class="lang-text tw">高密度覆蓋</span></h3>
index.html:656:                        <p class="text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed"><span class="lang-text cn">步行5分钟可达，骑行2分钟履约。彻底渗透高端住区与写字楼大堂，截流即时零散需求。</span><span class="lang-text en">5-min walk, 2-min bike delivery. Permeating lobbies and building floors to capture immediate needs.</span></p>
index.html:660:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4"><span class="lang-text cn">私域流量运营</span><span class="lang-text en">Private Traffic</span><span class="lang-text tw">私域運營</span></h3>
index.html:661:                        <p class="text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed"><span class="lang-text cn">每一位店长都是片区生活管家，通过社群营销、团购自提，深度绑定高净值用户的复购习惯。</span><span class="lang-text en">Store managers are block operators, driving retention through community chat groups and pick-up deals.</span></p>
index.html:665:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4"><span class="lang-text cn">极速响应网络</span><span class="lang-text en">Instant Response</span><span class="lang-text tw">極速響應</span></h3>
index.html:666:                        <p class="text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed"><span class="lang-text cn">高精尖选品，聚焦高频刚需，用最小的占地面积实现最大的履约密度，成为前置微仓网络。</span><span class="lang-text en">Curated inventory for high-frequency needs. Maximum fulfillment density in minimal retail footprint.</span></p>
index.html:679:                            <span class="lang-text cn">附近门店</span><span class="lang-text tw">附近門店</span><span class="lang-text en">Find a Location</span><span class="lang-text jp">店舗を探す</span><span class="lang-text kr">매장 찾기</span><span class="lang-text pt">Encontrar Local</span>
index.html:684:                            <span class="lang-text en">From Market to Mini, TomaGo uses visible neighborhood stores to power invisible operational capability. Each location is a retail point, a fulfillment node, and a local trust signal at once.</span>
index.html:698:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 display-en"><span class="lang-text cn">市集锚点</span><span class="lang-text tw">市集錨點</span><span class="lang-text en">Market Anchors</span><span class="lang-text jp">マーケット拠点</span><span class="lang-text kr">마켓 거점</span><span class="lang-text pt">Ancoras Market</span></h3>
index.html:699:                        <p class="text-slate-600 body-en"><span class="lang-text cn">布局在社区腹地和商圈边缘，负责品类深度、体验展示与区域订单中枢。</span><span class="lang-text tw">布局在社區腹地與商圈邊緣，負責品類深度、體驗展示與區域訂單中樞。</span><span class="lang-text en">Larger nodes for assortment depth, walk-in trust, and regional order consolidation.</span><span class="lang-text jp">品揃えと地域注文の中核を担う大型拠点です。</span><span class="lang-text kr">상품 깊이와 지역 주문을 담당하는 대형 거점입니다.</span><span class="lang-text pt">Nos maiores para sortimento e consolidacao regional de pedidos.</span></p>
index.html:703:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 display-en"><span class="lang-text cn">小店节点</span><span class="lang-text tw">小店節點</span><span class="lang-text en">Mini Nodes</span><span class="lang-text jp">ミニ拠点</span><span class="lang-text kr">미니 노드</span><span class="lang-text pt">Nos Mini</span></h3>
index.html:704:                        <p class="text-slate-600 body-en"><span class="lang-text cn">深入楼下、街角和办公区底层，承接高频补货、自提与最后 100 米响应。</span><span class="lang-text tw">深入樓下、街角與辦公區底層，承接高頻補貨、自提與最後 100 米回應。</span><span class="lang-text en">Smaller nodes embedded into the last 100 meters of everyday routines.</span><span class="lang-text jp">日常生活の最後の100メートルに入る小型拠点です。</span><span class="lang-text kr">생활 동선 마지막 100미터를 담당하는 소형 거점입니다.</span><span class="lang-text pt">Pontos menores para o ultimo trecho da rotina local.</span></p>
index.html:708:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 display-en"><span class="lang-text cn">本地节奏</span><span class="lang-text tw">本地節奏</span><span class="lang-text en">Local Rhythm</span><span class="lang-text jp">地域リズム</span><span class="lang-text kr">로컬 리듬</span><span class="lang-text pt">Ritmo Local</span></h3>
index.html:709:                        <p class="text-slate-600 body-en"><span class="lang-text cn">不同城区有不同的订单波峰、补货偏好和出行路径，门店网络因此必须具备密度与弹性。</span><span class="lang-text tw">不同城區有不同的訂單波峰、補貨偏好與出行路徑，門店網路因此必須具備密度與彈性。</span><span class="lang-text en">Every district has a different order rhythm, commute pattern, and replenishment profile.</span><span class="lang-text jp">地域ごとに需要の波と補充習慣が異なるため、店舗網にも柔軟性が必要です。</span><span class="lang-text kr">권역마다 주문 피크와 보충 습관이 달라 네트워크에도 탄력이 필요합니다.</span><span class="lang-text pt">Cada bairro tem seu proprio ritmo de pedidos e reposicao.</span></p>
index.html:722:                            <span class="lang-text cn">即时配送</span><span class="lang-text tw">即時配送</span><span class="lang-text en">Express Delivery</span><span class="lang-text jp">即時配送</span><span class="lang-text kr">빠른 배송</span><span class="lang-text pt">Entrega Expressa</span>
index.html:727:                            <span class="lang-text en">Express is not a simple transport layer. It is the result of stores, routing logic, order decomposition, and rider coordination working in sequence to produce sustainable speed.</span>
index.html:741:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 display-en"><span class="lang-text cn">系统拆单</span><span class="lang-text tw">系統拆單</span><span class="lang-text en">Order Decomposition</span><span class="lang-text jp">注文分解</span><span class="lang-text kr">주문 분해</span><span class="lang-text pt">Desdobramento</span></h3>
index.html:742:                        <p class="text-white/62 body-en"><span class="lang-text cn">订单进入系统后被自动判断来源门店、出货路径和最优骑手。</span><span class="lang-text tw">訂單進入系統後會自動判斷來源門店、出貨路徑與最優騎手。</span><span class="lang-text en">The system evaluates store source, picking path, and best rider assignment in real time.</span><span class="lang-text jp">店舗・経路・最適配達員を即時に判断します。</span><span class="lang-text kr">점포, 출고 경로, 최적 라이더를 실시간으로 판단합니다.</span><span class="lang-text pt">O sistema define loja, rota e entregador mais adequado em tempo real.</span></p>
index.html:746:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 display-en"><span class="lang-text cn">运力弹性</span><span class="lang-text tw">運力彈性</span><span class="lang-text en">Elastic Capacity</span><span class="lang-text jp">運力弾性</span><span class="lang-text kr">운력 탄성</span><span class="lang-text pt">Capacidade Elastico</span></h3>
index.html:747:                        <p class="text-white/62 body-en"><span class="lang-text cn">专职与灵活运力结合，在高峰、天气波动和节假日期间保持稳定履约。</span><span class="lang-text tw">專職與彈性運力結合，在高峰、天氣波動與節假日期間保持穩定履約。</span><span class="lang-text en">Dedicated and flexible rider pools stabilize delivery during peaks, holidays, and disruptions.</span><span class="lang-text jp">専任と柔軟運力を組み合わせ、変動期でも安定供給します。</span><span class="lang-text kr">전담과 유연 운력을 결합해 피크와 변수에도 안정성을 유지합니다.</span><span class="lang-text pt">Equipes fixas e flexiveis mantem estabilidade em picos e imprevistos.</span></p>
index.html:751:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 display-en"><span class="lang-text cn">体验闭环</span><span class="lang-text tw">體驗閉環</span><span class="lang-text en">Experience Loop</span><span class="lang-text jp">体験ループ</span><span class="lang-text kr">경험 루프</span><span class="lang-text pt">Loop de Experiencia</span></h3>
index.html:752:                        <p class="text-white/62 body-en"><span class="lang-text cn">用户看到的是准时送达，背后则是货、单、人、路全链条的时间压缩。</span><span class="lang-text tw">用戶看到的是準時送達，背後則是貨、單、人、路全鏈條的時間壓縮。</span><span class="lang-text en">What the user experiences as punctuality is actually time compression across goods, orders, people, and routes.</span><span class="lang-text jp">利用者が感じる時間厳守の裏には、全工程の圧縮があります。</span><span class="lang-text kr">사용자가 체감하는 정시성 뒤에는 전 과정의 시간 압축이 있습니다.</span><span class="lang-text pt">A pontualidade percebida vem da compressao do tempo em toda a cadeia.</span></p>
index.html:767:                            <span class="lang-text cn">商家入驻</span><span class="lang-text tw">商家入駐</span><span class="lang-text en">Partner with Us</span><span class="lang-text jp">パートナー募集</span><span class="lang-text kr">파트너 제휴</span><span class="lang-text pt">Seja Parceiro</span>
index.html:772:                            <span class="lang-text en">TomaGo offers a structured onboarding path for quality retailers, neighborhood brands, and local service businesses. We evaluate not only product fit, but operating model, fulfillment compatibility, and long-term user trust.</span>
index.html:785:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 display-en"><span class="lang-text cn">准入标准</span><span class="lang-text tw">準入標準</span><span class="lang-text en">Fit Criteria</span><span class="lang-text jp">加盟基準</span><span class="lang-text kr">입점 기준</span><span class="lang-text pt">Criterios</span></h3>
index.html:786:                        <p class="text-slate-600 body-en"><span class="lang-text cn">优先欢迎商品力强、复购高、供给稳定、用户评价好的商家。</span><span class="lang-text tw">優先歡迎商品力強、複購高、供給穩定、用戶評價好的商家。</span><span class="lang-text en">We prioritize strong assortment, stable supply, and high repeat-purchase potential.</span><span class="lang-text jp">供給の安定性と再購入性を重視します。</span><span class="lang-text kr">공급 안정성과 재구매 가능성을 중시합니다.</span><span class="lang-text pt">Priorizamos sortimento forte, oferta estavel e recompra.</span></p>
index.html:789:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 display-en"><span class="lang-text cn">上线流程</span><span class="lang-text tw">上線流程</span><span class="lang-text en">Go-Live Flow</span><span class="lang-text jp">立上线フロー</span><span class="lang-text kr">오픈 절차</span><span class="lang-text pt">Fluxo de Lancamento</span></h3>
index.html:790:                        <p class="text-slate-600 body-en"><span class="lang-text cn">从资料审核、合同确认到商品接入和运营准备，流程清晰且可复制。</span><span class="lang-text tw">從資料審核、合約確認到商品接入與營運準備，流程清晰且可複製。</span><span class="lang-text en">Qualification, commercial review, system setup, and launch preparation are handled in a structured sequence.</span><span class="lang-text jp">審査から接続、運営準備まで段階的に進みます。</span><span class="lang-text kr">심사, 연동, 운영 준비가 단계적으로 진행됩니다.</span><span class="lang-text pt">Triagem, revisao comercial, integracao e preparacao seguem uma sequencia clara.</span></p>
index.html:793:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 display-en"><span class="lang-text cn">长期协同</span><span class="lang-text tw">長期協同</span><span class="lang-text en">Long-Term Growth</span><span class="lang-text jp">長期協働</span><span class="lang-text kr">장기 협업</span><span class="lang-text pt">Crescimento Continuo</span></h3>
index.html:794:                        <p class="text-slate-600 body-en"><span class="lang-text cn">我们更看重长期关系，而不是一次性入驻，因此会围绕履约、营销和复购持续优化。</span><span class="lang-text tw">我們更看重長期關係，而不是一次性入駐，因此會圍繞履約、營銷與複購持續優化。</span><span class="lang-text en">The goal is not one-time onboarding, but sustained growth through operations, fulfillment, and retention.</span><span class="lang-text jp">単発契約ではなく継続的な成長を目指します。</span><span class="lang-text kr">일회성 입점보다 지속 성장 관계를 지향합니다.</span><span class="lang-text pt">Buscamos crescimento continuo, e nao apenas adesao pontual.</span></p>
index.html:810:                            <span class="lang-text cn">成为骑手</span><span class="lang-text tw">成為騎手</span><span class="lang-text en">Become a Rider</span><span class="lang-text jp">配達員になる</span><span class="lang-text kr">라이더 지원</span><span class="lang-text pt">Seja um Entregador</span>
index.html:815:                            <span class="lang-text en">Riders are more than couriers. They are the final human touchpoint of the instant retail system, which is why TomaGo focuses on safety, consistency, service discipline, and room to grow.</span>
index.html:825:                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 display-en"><span class="lang-text cn">入职路径</span><span class="lang-text tw">入職路徑</span><span class="lang-text en">Entry Path</span><span class="lang-text jp">参加導線</span><span class="lang-text kr">입직 경로</span><span class="lang-text pt">Caminho de Entrada</span></h3>
index.html:826:                        <p class="text-slate-600 body-en"><span class="lang-text cn">认证、培训、设备准备与站点分配形成清晰的上岗流程。</span><span class="lang-text tw">認證、培訓、設備準備與站點分配形成清晰的上崗流程。</span><span class="lang-text en">Verification, training, equipment readiness, and site assignment follow one streamlined process.</span><span class="lang-text jp">認証・研修・拠点配置まで明確な流れがあります。</span><span class="lang-text kr">인증, 교육, 장비 준비, 거점 배치가 하나의 절차로 이어집니다.</span><span class="lang-text pt">Verificacao, treinamento e alocacao seguem um fluxo claro.</span></p>
